{"word":"ἐξαρτύω","slug":"ἐξαρτύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξαρτύω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ύσω</el>) </el><p/><i>to get ready, equip thoroughly, fit out</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to get ready for oneself, fit out</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <el>ἐξαρτύεται γαμεῖν</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be got ready</i>, <el>πάντα σφι ἐξήρτυτο</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—in <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a>, <i>equipt, harnessed</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> rei, <i>furnished</i> or <i>provided with</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/>"}]}